Privacy Policy for Selling Weight

Effective Date: 1 Oct, 2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to Selling Weight! We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our application.

2. Information We Collect

Selling Weight does not collect any personal data from users. The app is designed solely for recording and managing cash and inventory without any actual transactions or money flow.

3. Subscription Plans

To access features of the app, users may subscribe to either a monthly or yearly plan. The payment processing is handled through third-party services, and we do not store any payment information.

4. Data Usage

Since we do not collect or store any personal information, we do not use your data for any purpose, nor do we share it with third parties. The app is designed for your personal use, allowing you to manage cash, add products, and view transaction history.

5. Security

While we do not collect personal data, we are committed to ensuring that your experience with Selling Weight is secure. We implement reasonable security measures to protect the app from unauthorized access and data breaches.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in the app. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at connorjbuban@gmail.com

8. Acceptance of This Policy

By using Selling Weight, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.

